Title: Enacts the interstate nurse licensure compact and the advanced practice registered nurse compact
Summary: Adopts the interstate nurse licensure compact (Part A); adopts the advanced practice registered nurse compact (Part B).
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to adopting the interstate nurse licensure compact (Part A); and to amend the education law, in relation to adopting the advanced practice registered nurse compact (Part B)
